HEADWORD: Colstaff
<hw>Col"staff`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>col</ets>
neck + E. <ets>staff</ets>. Cf. <er>Coll</er>.]</ety> <def>A staff by
